&lt;li&gt;Experience with reporting and business intelligence software such as Tableau, Power BI, Grafana, Superset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with tools such as Airflow and NiFi.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
