&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An undergraduate degree or diploma&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5 - 8+ years&#39; experience coordinating between multiple teams to deliver software products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A technical background, with experience in:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3rd Party integrations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;RESTful APIs, JSON/XML and cloud technologies&lt;/li&gt;
